These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 4

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-1::.
Flower: amaryllis, tulip, marigold, dahlia
Food: grapefruit, strawberry, blueberry, lemon
1. Food:lemon is on the left of Flower:marigold##1
2. Flower:amaryllis is on the left of Food:strawberry##1
3. Flower:dahlia is in an odd position##4
4. Food:blueberry is on the left or right of Food:lemon##3
5. Flower:amaryllis is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|            |  1  |   2    |   3   |    4     |
| Flower   | amaryllis | tulip | dahlia | marigold |
| Food        | grapefruit | strawberry   | lemon | blueberry    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-2::.
Birthday: december, august, june, july
Color: black, light-blue, azure, blood-red
1. Birthday:august is on the left of Birthday:july##1
2. Color:black is on the left of Color:azure##1
3. Color:azure is in an odd position##4
4. Color:black == Birthday:december##1
5. Color:light-blue is on the right of Color:azure##1
6. Color:black == Birthday:december##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |   2    |    3     |     4     |
| Birthday   | june | december  | august  | july |
| Color   | blood-red    | black | azure | light-blue    |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-3::.
Sport: skateboarding, cricket, basketball, snowboarding
Cigar: davidoff, pall-mall, aristoff, bolivar
1. Sport:snowboarding is on the left or right of Cigar:bolivar##3
2. Sport:basketball is in an even position##4
3. Cigar:bolivar is on the left or right of Sport:cricket##3
4. Cigar:bolivar is on the right of Cigar:aristoff##1
5. Cigar:davidoff is in an odd position##4
6. Sport:cricket is on the right of Sport:basketball##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |     3     |      4      |
| Sport          | snowboarding | basketball | cricket    | skateboarding      |
| Cigar   | aristoff        | bolivar     | davidoff | pall-mall |

