2. Flower:azalea is on the left of Flower:rose##1
3. Cigar:prince is in an odd position##4
4. Cigar:tiparillo is on the left of Cigar:siglo##1
5. Cigar:tiparillo is on the right of Flower:rose##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |    2    |    3    |    4    |
