.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-5::.
Game: domino, mah-jongg, monopoly, bridge
Movie-Genre: thriller, spy, satire, adventure
1. Game:monopoly is on the right of Movie-Genre:adventure##1
2. Movie-Genre:spy == Game:bridge##1
3. Movie-Genre:satire is on the right of Game:domino##1
4. Game:mah-jongg is on the far left##1
5. Game:monopoly is in an odd position##4
6. Movie-Genre:thriller is on the far left or far right##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |    2    |   3    |     4      |
| Game   | mah-jongg  | domino    | monopoly   | bridge       |
| Movie-Genre   | thriller | adventure | satire | spy |

