2. Birthday:october is on the right of Birthday:september##1
3. Music-Genre:folk is between Music-Genre:rock and Birthday:march##2
4. Music-Genre:folk is in an odd position##4
5. Birthday:march == Music-Genre:electronic##1

.:: Answer ::.
|        |     1      |    2    |    3    |   4    |
| Birthday   | july | september   | october | march |
| Music-Genre    | punk     | rock | folk     | electronic  |

