.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-4-10::.
City: rome, venice, nizza, berlin
House: craftsman, art-deco, gothic-revival, cape-cod
1. City:rome == House:cape-cod##1
2. House:craftsman is on the right of City:rome##1
3. House:cape-cod is between House:craftsman and City:nizza##2
4. City:rome is in an odd position##4
5. House:cape-cod is on the left or right of House:craftsman##3
6. City:venice is on the left or right of House:art-deco##3

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2    |      3      |    4     |
| City      | venice       | nizza   | rome | berlin |
| House   | gothic-revival | art-deco | cape-cod        | craftsman    |

