2. Music-Genre:rock is on the left or right of Music-Genre:country##3
3. Music-Genre:ambient is on the far left or far right##3
4. Sport:soccer is on the left of Sport:badminton##1
5. Sport:badminton is on the right of Music-Genre:country##1
6. Sport:soccer is in an even position##4
7. Sport:surfing == Music-Genre:disco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|            |   1   |   2    |     3      |   4   |
| Music-Genre   | ambient | country    | rock       | disco |
| Sport       | cycling  | soccer | badminton | surfing  |

