2. Color:light-blue is on the left or right of Birthday:february##3
3. Birthday:november is between Color:brown and Birthday:february##2
4. Color:light-blue is on the far left or far right##3
5. Birthday:august is on the right of Color:pink##1
6. Birthday:august is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |    2    |         3          |    4    |
| Color         | brown | aquamarine   | pink | light-blue |
| Birthday   | september          | november | february         | august  |

 